## Tenant Isolation

- Data isolation at storage and query level
- No cross-tenant data leakage; no shared mutable state
- Tenant context in every request; fail closed on missing context

## Audit & Immutability

- Every mutation produces an audit event; no silent overwrites
- Versioning explicit; document history traceable
- Tamper-evident logs; append-only audit trail
